  %% Diagram 61: Vendor Inventory Replenishment and Lead-Time Learning Flow

  Monitor[Monitor stock + forecast context]
  ROP[Compute smart reorder point]
  Breach{stock_on_hand <= ROP?}

  Recommend[Issue reorder recommendation]
  PlacePO[Vendor places supplier order]
  Receive[Receive stock delivery]
  Learn[Update learned lead-time model\nfrom expected vs actual receipt]
  Sync[Inventory updated and alerts cleared]

  NoAction[No urgent reorder action]

  SupplierHistory{Supplier lead-time history available?}
  DefaultLT[Use default lead-time baseline\nmark lower confidence]

  Delay{Delivery delayed?}
  Escalate[Escalate urgency and suggest safety buffer]

  Monitor --> SupplierHistory
  SupplierHistory -- Yes --> ROP
  SupplierHistory -- No --> DefaultLT --> ROP

  ROP --> Breach
  Breach -- No --> NoAction
  Breach -- Yes --> Recommend --> PlacePO --> Receive --> Delay

  Delay -- Yes --> Escalate --> Learn
  Delay -- No --> Learn

  Learn --> Sync
